《'''2020年聯合王國內部市場法'''》（{{lang-en|United Kingdom Internal Market Act 2020}}），是一條[[英國國會法令|英國國會法令]]，旨為[[英國脫歐|脫歐協議過渡期]]後在[[英國的構成國|構成國]]間設立貿易框架，以及在運作上限制某些已被[[英國的權力下放|權力下放]]至構成國政府的權限。

[[鲍里斯·约翰逊|约翰逊]]政府多次稱之為「安全網」（{{lang|en|safety net}}）<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.euronews.com/2020/09/09/watch-live-mps-set-to-grill-pm-johnson-over-controversial-brexit-plan|title=UK's new Brexit bill is 'legal safety net', PM Johnson says|date=2020-09-09|work=[[欧洲新闻台|欧洲新闻台]]|language=en|accessdate=2020-11-11|archive-date=2020-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201116042921/https://www.euronews.com/2020/09/09/watch-live-mps-set-to-grill-pm-johnson-over-controversial-brexit-plan|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-politics-54318987|title=Michael Gove: Brexit provisions to stay in Internal Market Bill|date=2020-09-28|work=[[英國廣播公司新聞|BBC新聞]]|language=en|accessdate=2020-11-11|archive-date=2020-12-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201211071202/https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-politics-54318987|dead-url=no}}</ref>，以確保在與歐盟的貿易談判失敗下，仍能保護全國內部市場的完整性。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.express.co.uk/news/politics/1358159/Boris-Johnson-house-of-lords-block-internal-market-bill-latest|title=Boris issues furious warning over Lords' new Brexit block - Internal Market bill is DEAD|date=2020-11-10|work=[[每日快報|每日快報]]|language=en|accessdate=2020-11-11|archive-date=2020-11-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201125111743/https://www.express.co.uk/news/politics/1358159/Boris-Johnson-house-of-lords-block-internal-market-bill-latest|dead-url=no}}</ref>然而，構成國政府批評此法案會令西敏政府重新中央集權，令權力下放變成「權力上繳」。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.centreonconstitutionalchange.ac.uk/news-and-opinion/internal-market-bill-implications-devolution|title=The Internal Market Bill: implications for devolution|date=2020-09-11|website=Centre on Constitutional Change|language=en|first=Nicola|last=McEwen|accessdate=2020-11-11|archive-date=2020-11-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201128102908/https://www.centreonconstitutionalchange.ac.uk/news-and-opinion/internal-market-bill-implications-devolution|dead-url=no}}</ref>另外，儘管[[英国宪法|英国宪法]]的核心原則是[[議會主權|議會主權]]，國內法律可凌駕國際法，但法案中的個別條文亦因違反作為[[条约|条约]]的《英國脫歐協議》，被視為不尊重國際法精神，而惹起有關[[法治|法治]]的爭議。法律界持有不少反對聲音，當中包括前任[[英国最高法院|最高法院院長]][[廖柏嘉|廖柏嘉勳爵]]，說如果對政府運作的[[司法覆核|司法覆核]]權利被剝奪，那等同處於一個「獨裁政權」、「暴政」。<ref>{{cite news | title= Brexit strategy risks UK 'dictatorship', says ex-president of supreme court. Lord Neuberger condemns internal market bill for exempting some of its powers from legal challenge | url= https://www.theguardian.com/law/2020/oct/07/brexit-strategy-puts-uk-on-slippery-slope-to-tyranny-lawyers-told | work= [[衛報|衛報]] | first= Owen | last= Bowcott | date= 2020-10-07 | language= en | accessdate= 2020-11-11 | archive-date= 2020-12-16 | archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20201216060245/https://www.theguardian.com/law/2020/oct/07/brexit-strategy-puts-uk-on-slippery-slope-to-tyranny-lawyers-told | dead-url= no }}</ref>

由于法案多次被上议院否决，英国政府对法案进行了修改，使其更加灵活，同时也删去了第五部分涉及北爱尔兰的争议条款。法令最终于2020年12月17日获得[[御准|御准]]。

== 具爭議的部分 ==
法案具爭議的條文主要圍繞北愛爾蘭和國家援助，特別是與《北愛爾蘭議定書》有關的第五部分（第40至第45條）。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-politics-54118963|title=The week ahead in Parliament|date=2020-09-11|work=[[英國廣播公司新聞|BBC新聞]]|language=en|accessdate=2020-11-11|archive-date=2020-09-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200917194729/https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-politics-54118963|dead-url=no}}</ref>因此部分，[[英國上議院|上議院]]在二讀議案增加遺憾議案<ref>{{cite web|url=https://hansard.parliament.uk/Lords/2020-10-20/debates/C6281305-A100-4FE1-90FA-2FD74B9C0C31/UnitedKingdomInternalMarketBill#division-30110|title=United Kingdom Internal Market Bill|website=英國國會議事錄|date=2020-10-20|accessdate=2020-11-11|archive-date=2020-11-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201117090831/https://hansard.parliament.uk/Lords/2020-10-20/debates/C6281305-A100-4FE1-90FA-2FD74B9C0C31/UnitedKingdomInternalMarketBill#division-30110|dead-url=no}}</ref>，更在全體委員會階段否決第42至第45條，聯同有關國家援助的第六部分，共否決了六條條文。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://hansard.parliament.uk/Lords/2020-11-09/debates/67BF795E-B630-4922-B1AB-2A0197888C5C/UnitedKingdomInternalMarketBill#division-30456|title=United Kingdom Internal Market Bill|website=英國國會議事錄|date=2020-11-09|accessdate=2020-11-11|archive-date=2020-12-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201205132411/https://hansard.parliament.uk/Lords/2020-11-09/debates/67BF795E-B630-4922-B1AB-2A0197888C5C/UnitedKingdomInternalMarketBill#division-30456|dead-url=no}}</ref>

