=== 國際 ===
==== 歐盟 ====
如果英國境內能沒規限地與北愛爾蘭進行貿易，海外貨品便可入口至更低關稅的英國，再通過北愛－愛爾蘭關口進入歐盟，逃避歐盟關稅區，故此在脫歐談判中歐盟一直未能讓步，此安排亦載入已成為條約的脫歐協議中。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://blogs.lse.ac.uk/brexit/2020/10/19/how-does-the-uk-internal-market-bill-relate-to-northern-ireland/|title=How does the UK Internal Market Bill relate to Northern Ireland?|first=Katy|last=Hayward|date=2020-10-19|language=en|website=[[倫敦政治經濟學院|倫敦政治經濟學院]]網誌|accessdate=2020-11-11|archive-date=2020-11-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201118060625/https://blogs.lse.ac.uk/brexit/2020/10/19/how-does-the-uk-internal-market-bill-relate-to-northern-ireland/|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[欧盟委员会主席|欧盟委员会主席]][[乌尔苏拉·冯德莱恩|乌尔苏拉·冯德莱恩]]警告首相[[鲍里斯·约翰逊|鲍里斯·约翰逊]]，英國執行脫歐協議是所有未來合作關係的先決條件。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/politics/2020/sep/07/michel-barnier-worried-by-no-10-plans-to-renege-on-brexit-deal|title=Von der Leyen warns UK against breaking international law over Brexit deal|date=2020-09-07|language=en|work=[[衛報|衛報]]|accessdate=2020-11-11|archive-date=2020-12-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201217125341/https://www.theguardian.com/politics/2020/sep/07/michel-barnier-worried-by-no-10-plans-to-renege-on-brexit-deal|dead-url=no}}</ref>2020年10月1日，[[欧洲联盟委员会|欧洲联盟委员会]]為英國拒絕移除違反條約的條文，而發出正式通函，是為控訴違約的第一步。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://ec.europa.eu/commission/presscorner/detail/en/ip_20_1798?cookies=disabled|title=Withdrawal Agreement: European Commission sends letter of formal notice to the United Kingdom for breach of its obligations|location=[[布鲁塞尔|布鲁塞尔]]|website=[[欧洲联盟委员会|欧洲联盟委员会]]|date=2020-10-01|language=en|accessdate=2020-11-11|archive-date=2020-11-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201117103257/https://ec.europa.eu/commission/presscorner/detail/en/ip_20_1798?cookies=disabled|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/politics/2020/oct/01/brexit-eu-launches-legal-action-against-uk-for-breaching-withdrawal-agreement|title=Brexit: EU launches legal action against UK for breaching withdrawal agreement|date=2020-10-01|language=en|work=[[衛報|衛報]]|accessdate=2020-11-11|archive-date=2020-12-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201217125215/https://www.theguardian.com/politics/2020/oct/01/brexit-eu-launches-legal-action-against-uk-for-breaching-withdrawal-agreement|dead-url=no}}</ref>

